            <h3>Deliverables</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Sitemap + information architecture</li>
              <li>Page templates (Home, Services, Case Studies, About, Contact)</li>
              <li>Lead capture/contact flow</li>
              <li>On-page SEO foundations + performance-first build</li>
              <li>Portable, repo-based workflow for long-term ownership</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Outcome</h3>
            <p>Built to convert inbound consulting leads; structured for future capability statement content and compliance-ready content ops.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Placeholder Case Study 2 -->
      <div class="case-study-card">
        <div class="case-study-image">
          <div class="placeholder-image">
            <span>Project Name</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <h2>Project #2</h2>
          <p class="case-subtitle">Coming Soon</p>
          
          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Context</h3>
            <p>Add your second case study here with details about the project context and goals.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Role</h3>
            <p>Describe your specific role and responsibilities in this project.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Deliverables</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Key deliverable 1</li>
              <li>Key deliverable 2</li>
              <li>Key deliverable 3</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Outcome</h3>
            <p>Describe the measurable results or qualitative impact of the work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Placeholder Case Study 3 -->
      <div class="case-study-card">
        <div class="case-study-image">
          <div class="placeholder-image">
            <span>Project Name</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <h2>Project #3</h2>
          <p class="case-subtitle">Coming Soon</p>
          
          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Context</h3>
            <p>Add your third case study here with details about the project context and goals.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="case-section">
            <h3>Role</h3>
            <p>Describe your specific role and responsibilities in this project.</p>
